13
00:00:20,240 --> 00:00:22,640
[-Jinwoo: Wow, interesting.
-Seungho: They split them up instantly.]

14
00:00:22,640 --> 00:00:23,180
[Jinwoo: Exactly.]

15
00:00:23,980 --> 00:00:25,580
