18
00:00:31,720 --> 00:00:33,660
[Hyeyeon: Sujin is just so cute.]

19
00:00:33,660 --> 00:00:35,860
[Hyeyeon: I was literally just thinking,]

20
00:00:35,860 --> 00:00:39,340
