147
00:05:38,960 --> 00:05:40,560
[Yongkyu: I'm half and half.]

148
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:41,630
[Yongkyu: I plan when I need to.]

149
00:05:41,630 --> 00:05:42,430
[Yongkyu: Otherwise, I just wing it.]

150
00:05:42,430 --> 00:05:45,370
[Yongkyu: If my partner doesn't plan, I will.]

151
00:05:45,900 --> 00:05:48,570
[Yongkyu: If they plan, I just follow along.]

152
