[Yongkyu: Yeah, 6 people means 6 eggs.]

928
00:39:53,360 --> 00:39:58,160
[A sudden debate over the egg count begins]

929
00:39:54,900 --> 00:39:55,600
I was just spitballing.

930
00:39:55,600 --> 00:39:56,300
6 people means 6 eggs, obviously.

931
00:39:56,300 --> 00:39:57,300
One per person?

932
00:39:58,160 --> 00:40:01,900
[Yongkyu: But if we cook exactly
by head count, it might be a bit too much.]

933
00:40:01,540 --> 00:40:02,180
Really?

934
00:40:01,900 --> 00:40:04,570
[Hyeyeon: I always...]

935
00:40:04,570 --> 00:40:06,710
[Hyeyeon: Even if I'm eating alone,
I use 3 eggs.]

936
00:40:06,710 --> 00:40:08,310
[-Yongkyu: Really?
-Hyeyeon: Yeah.]

937
00:40:08,310 --> 00:40:09,910
[Yongkyu: That's way too many eggs then.]

938
00:40:09,910 --> 00:40:12,040
[Hyeyeon: Is it? Let's just do 10 eggs then?]

939
00:40:12,040 --> 00:40:13,650
[Yongkyu: Alright, let's do 10 eggs.]

940
00:40:13,460 --> 00:40:14,060
Crack them.

941
00:40:13,650 --> 00:40:16,050
[-Hyeyeon: How about 9?
-Seungho: 9, 9.]

942
00:40:16,050 --> 00:40:18,180
[-Jinwoo: How about 9.5? 9.5 eggs.
-Hyeyeon: Sure, go ahead and crack them.]

943
00:40:18,180 --> 00:40:21,120
[-Jinwoo: 9.5?
-Hyeyeon: Go ahead.]

944
00:40:18,540 --> 00:40:19,470
-9.5? -Go ahead.

945
00:40:21,120 --> 00:40:22,190
[Jinwoo: Wait, but...]

946
00:40:22,190 --> 00:40:25,460
[-Jinwoo: Do the whites and yolks go together?
-Yongkyu: Yeah, just mix them all up.]

947
00:40:25,460 --> 00:40:29,660
[Cooking for the first time in his entire life...]

948
00:40:25,460 --> 00:40:26,260
How else were you gonna separate them?

949
00:40:26,260 --> 00:40:27,060
No, I mean...

950
00:40:27,060 --> 00:40:28,220
I thought we had to separate them,

951
00:40:28,220 --> 00:40:29,660
like when making cookies.

952
00:40:29,660 --> 00:40:32,060
[Hyeyeon: Can you handle this?]

953
00:40:32,060 --> 00:40:33,670
[Seungho: If I crack them,
the shells are definitely getting in.]

954
00:40:33,670 --> 00:40:36,600
[-Jinwoo: Oh! A shell fell in.
-Seungho: I think I can do this.]

955
00:40:36,600 --> 00:40:38,200
[Jinwoo: Hold on.]

956
00:40:38,380 --> 00:40:39,340
I washed my hands.

957
00:40:38,470 --> 00:40:41,140
[Cleaning it up himself, haha]

958
00:40:39,860 --> 00:40:40,980
How is it?

959
00:40:41,140 --> 00:40:43,010
[-Seungho: Let me try one.
-Jinwoo: Alright, go ahead.]

960
00:40:43,010 --> 00:40:44,080
[Seungho: Cooking is just not my...]

961
00:40:44,080 --> 00:40:45,410
[Jinwoo: Let's see if you have hidden talent.]

962
00:40:45,460 --> 00:40:47,180
[Crack, crack]

963
00:40:48,880 --> 00:40:51,020
[-Hyeyeon: Ooh, look at that talent.
-Seungho: Better than him?]

964
00:40:51,020 --> 00:40:53,420
[-Jinwoo: Oh! There's a shell in there.
-Seungho: Wait, I don't think so.]

965
00:40:53,420 --> 00:40:54,750
[Seungho: How do I get it out?]

966
00:40:54,750 --> 00:40:57,160
[Hyeyeon: Just wash your hands and take it out.]

967
00:40:57,160 --> 00:40:58,540
[-Seungho: Really?
-Hyeyeon: Yeah.]

968
00:40:58,780 --> 00:41:01,460
[Careful]

969
00:41:01,500 --> 00:41:04,630
[Seungho: Since I rarely ever cook,]

970
00:41:04,630 --> 00:41:07,300
[Seungho: the process itself was pretty fun.]

971
00:41:07,300 --> 00:41:09,440
[Seungho: Making a meal here]

972
00:41:09,440 --> 00:41:11,840
[Seungho: with new people]

973
00:41:11,840 --> 00:41:13,440
[Seungho: was honestly interesting.]

974
00:41:13,440 --> 00:41:15,040
[Hyeyeon: Still haven't gotten it out?]

975
00:41:15,040 --> 00:41:15,840
[Hyeyeon: Let me try.]

976
00:41:15,840 --> 00:41:19,040
[Seungho: There were three pieces.
Got 2 out already.]

977
00:41:19,040 --> 00:41:21,180
[Jinwoo: I win. I only dropped one piece.]

978
00:41:21,180 --> 00:41:22,780
[Hyeyeon: Okay, that's a bit of a stretch.]

979
00:41:23,940 --> 00:41:26,380
[But a small mistake like this is fine.]

980
00:41:26,700 --> 00:41:28,060
Did we settle on the egg count? 10?

981
00:41:27,850 --> 00:41:30,520
[The head chef steps in to speed things up]

982
00:41:28,340 --> 00:41:29,340
-9. -9.

983
00:41:30,520 --> 00:41:32,930
[Ooh, professional]

984
00:41:34,820 --> 00:41:36,740
[Skillful]

985
00:41:36,260 --> 00:41:38,180
Cracking them against each other.

986
00:41:38,180 --> 00:41:39,220
Impressive.

987
00:41:40,400 --> 00:41:44,140
[Seungho: Looks exactly like
how I dropped the shell, though.]

988
00:41:44,670 --> 00:41:47,070
[-Jinwoo: Wow, thanks.
-Yongkyu: Looks like too much.]

989
00:41:47,220 --> 00:41:48,460
-Get it out. -Okay.

990
00:41:49,740 --> 00:41:52,680
[-Jinwoo: Can't tolerate a single bit of shell.
-Seungho: Oh, wait.]

991
00:41:52,680 --> 00:41:55,610
[Seungho: My bad.]

992
00:41:55,610 --> 00:41:56,680
[Yongkyu: Are you guys Dumb and Dumber?]

993
00:41:56,680 --> 00:41:58,820
[Jinwoo: No way, we're doing great right now.]

994
00:41:57,900 --> 00:41:58,840
Are you sure you aren't Dumb and Dumber?

995
00:41:58,820 --> 00:42:00,690
[-Jinwoo: We're killing it.
-Seungho: I got this.]

996
00:41:58,840 --> 00:41:59,780
I got this.

997
00:42:01,860 --> 00:42:02,620
Alright, all good.

998
00:42:02,620 --> 00:42:03,180
Done?

999
00:42:03,620 --> 00:42:05,490
[-Seungho: We're good, we're good.
-Jinwoo: Honestly, this looks great.]

1000
00:42:05,490 --> 00:42:06,500
[Jinwoo: We just whisk it, right?]

1001
00:42:06,820 --> 00:42:08,380
[Whisking]

1002
00:42:08,380 --> 00:42:11,630
[Seungho: Just stir it?]

1003
00:42:11,630 --> 00:42:12,700
[Jinwoo: How is it?]

1004
00:42:12,700 --> 00:42:14,570
[Yongkyu: Perfect.]

1005
00:42:13,860 --> 00:42:14,790
-Right? -Right?

1006
00:42:15,020 --> 00:42:15,580
Almost done.

1007
00:42:15,220 --> 00:42:16,580
[Proud]

1008
00:42:15,580 --> 00:42:16,980
-Good to go. -Right?

1009
00:42:16,680 --> 00:42:18,820
[-Seungho: Ready?
-Yongkyu: Yep, all good.]

1010
00:42:18,820 --> 00:42:22,290
[Seungho: I was clumsy
with even the simple tasks,]

1011
00:42:22,290 --> 00:42:26,030
[Seungho: but Yongkyu didn't mind at all.]

1012
00:42:26,030 --> 00:42:29,760
[Seungho: Instead, he watched out for us,
which was really nice.]

1013
00:42:29,760 --> 00:42:33,230
[Jinwoo: Anything else to do? Bowls?]

1014
00:42:33,230 --> 00:42:35,630
[-Yongkyu: The rice...
-Jinwoo: Microwave it?]

1015
00:42:35,630 --> 00:42:39,370
[-Yongkyu: Please heat up the rice.
-Jinwoo: Got it.]

1016
00:42:39,370 --> 00:42:42,310
[Yongkyu: 8 packs should be enough, right?
Since they're 200g each.]

1017
00:42:43,380 --> 00:42:45,480
[Jinwoo: That feels a bit short.]

1018
00:42:45,480 --> 00:42:47,240
[-Jinwoo: What do you think?
-Yongkyu: 10 packs?]

1019
00:42:47,840 --> 00:42:50,050
[The quantity debate begins again]

1020
00:42:49,180 --> 00:42:49,820
10 packs.

1021
00:42:50,050 --> 00:42:52,720
[He was a military cook, a military cook!]

1022
00:42:51,660 --> 00:42:52,720
-Exactly. -10 packs.

1023
00:42:52,720 --> 00:42:55,920
[Hyeyeon: This is literally my first time
microwaving 10 packs of rice.]

1024
00:42:56,990 --> 00:42:59,120
[Yongkyu: No matter how I look at it,
that's too many eggs.]

1025
00:42:59,120 --> 00:43:02,590
[Hyeyeon: No it's not,
we're pouring it over the top.]

1026
00:43:02,590 --> 00:43:05,000
[Yongkyu: It feels like the eggs
are taking over the dish.]

1027
00:43:05,000 --> 00:43:06,600
[-Hyeyeon: Trust me, it tastes amazing this way.
-Yongkyu: It's turning into an omelet.]

1028
00:43:06,600 --> 00:43:09,000
[-Seungho: Really?
-Hyeyeon: It tastes amazing this way.]

1029
00:43:09,000 --> 00:43:10,870
[Hyeyeon: Don't regret it when you eat it.]

1030
00:43:11,140 --> 00:43:13,270
[Seungho: Don't regret it?]

1031
00:43:13,270 --> 00:43:16,740
[-Seungho: Is that the right word?
-Hyeyeon: Wait, that's not what I meant.]

1032
00:43:16,740 --> 00:43:17,540
[Hyeyeon: Perfect!]

1033
00:43:17,540 --> 00:43:19,410
[Hyeyeon: Look, it's just right.]

1034
00:43:19,410 --> 00:43:20,750
[Hyeyeon: Look at it when you scoop it up.]

1035
00:43:20,750 --> 00:43:22,350
[-Seungho: Wow, actually...
-Hyeyeon: Right?]

1036
00:43:22,350 --> 00:43:25,820
[-Seungho: ...it looks pretty legit.
-Hyeyeon: See? It's egg drop soup.]

1037
00:43:28,750 --> 00:43:30,890
[Hyeyeon: What do you think?]

1038
00:43:31,690 --> 00:43:34,630
[Yongkyu: Just need some pepper
and hot peppers now.]

1039
00:43:35,960 --> 00:43:37,560
[Hyeyeon: Want a taste?]

1040
00:43:37,560 --> 00:43:39,700
[Seungho: Sure.]

1041
00:43:39,700 --> 00:43:41,830
[Hyeyeon: It's hot.]

1042
00:43:41,100 --> 00:43:42,020
It needs more pepper.

1043
00:43:41,830 --> 00:43:42,630
[Hyeyeon: How is it?]

1044
00:43:42,650 --> 00:43:44,790
[Seungho: Not bad, but it's a bit...]

1045
00:43:44,790 --> 00:43:45,860
[-Yongkyu: A bit bland, right?
-Seungho: Yeah, exactly.]

1046
00:43:45,860 --> 00:43:47,730
[Yongkyu: Pepper, pepper. Yeah,
add some pepper.]

1047
00:43:48,180 --> 00:43:51,100
[Hyeyeon subtly feeding Seungho]

1048
00:43:51,200 --> 00:43:54,740
[Hyeyeon: That? Flirting, obviously.]

1049
00:43:54,860 --> 00:43:57,460
[Seungho is handsome, after all.]

1050
00:43:58,140 --> 00:44:01,580
[While the assistants set the table...]

1051
00:44:01,580 --> 00:44:04,460
[Smoothly]

1052
00:44:04,900 --> 00:44:07,820
[Hyeyeon and Yongkyu officially
start the Kimchi fried rice]

1053
00:44:07,820 --> 00:44:09,980
[Hyeyeon: You're really good at cooking.]

1054
00:44:09,980 --> 00:44:12,740
[Yongkyu: It's honestly been forever
since I last cooked.]

1055
00:44:13,040 --> 00:44:17,310
[Hyeyeon: Since you said you were only confident
with Kimchi fried rice,]

1056
00:44:17,310 --> 00:44:20,510
[Hyeyeon: I figured you
weren't much of a cook.]

1057
00:44:21,310 --> 00:44:25,310
[Yongkyu: Hyeyeon is really warm and friendly.]

1058
00:44:25,310 --> 00:44:28,250
[Yongkyu: Even when cooking with the others...]

1059
00:44:28,250 --> 00:44:29,590
[Yongkyu: She'll come help too.]

1060
00:44:29,590 --> 00:44:33,860
[Yongkyu: She takes the initiative
and keeps trying to pitch in.]

1061
00:44:33,860 --> 00:44:37,060
[Yongkyu: She seems really nice.
Doesn't make you feel pressured.]

1062
00:44:37,060 --> 00:44:41,330
[She's great. I'm kinda curious about her]

1063
00:44:39,940 --> 00:44:41,500
That's what I think.

1064
00:44:42,420 --> 00:44:45,980
All he said was that he can
only make kimchi fried rice.

1065
00:44:45,870 --> 00:44:49,070
[Hyeyeon: I thought he'd just chop up
some kimchi and stir-fry it real quick.]

1066
00:44:49,070 --> 00:44:52,540
[Hyeyeon: Surprisingly, he actually has
opinions and even tastes for seasoning.]

1067
00:44:52,540 --> 00:44:56,550
[Hyeyeon: He gives directions too,
trying to take on more work himself.]

1068
00:44:56,550 --> 00:44:59,750
[Hyeyeon: So it took a lot of
pressure off me.]

1069
00:44:59,750 --> 00:45:01,700
[Hyeyeon: As for the other two...]

1070
00:45:01,700 --> 00:45:04,220
[Staring blankly]

1071
00:45:05,220 --> 00:45:08,740
[-Hyeyeon: You two are really...
-Jinwoo: Ah, it fell!]

1072
00:45:08,780 --> 00:45:12,700
[Seungho and Jinwoo,
making Hyeyeon crack up]

1073
00:45:09,540 --> 00:45:10,740
[Geez... is it good?]

1074
00:45:11,000 --> 00:45:12,700
-This one's the lighter taste.
-Good, good.

1075
00:45:12,700 --> 00:45:16,180
[Hyeyeon: They kept me entertained
right next to me.]

1076
00:45:16,180 --> 00:45:18,700
[Hyeyeon: It felt fun
and really relaxed.]

1077
00:45:19,160 --> 00:45:21,300
[-Hyeyeon: Can we add some cheese?
-Yongkyu: Cheese?]

1078
00:45:21,300 --> 00:45:23,440
[-Jinwoo: There actually is cheese in the fridge.
-Hyeyeon: Right? I saw it too.]

1079
00:45:23,440 --> 00:45:24,240
[Yongkyu: Alright then.]

1080
00:45:24,240 --> 00:45:27,970
[-Yongkyu: We're making two portions in that pan anyway.
-Hyeyeon: Ah, two portions?]

1081
00:45:27,970 --> 00:45:30,060
[Yongkyu: One with cheese,
and the other...]

1082
00:45:30,060 --> 00:45:31,500
[Jinwoo: Oh, okay.]

1083
00:45:31,500 --> 00:45:34,380
[Hyeyeon: Okay. You don't
like it with cheese?]

1084
00:45:34,400 --> 00:45:36,000
[Yongkyu: Ah... I... well...]

1085
00:45:36,000 --> 00:45:37,870
[Yongkyu: I want it plain.]

1086
00:45:39,200 --> 00:45:43,210
[First up: Yongkyu's signature
plain kimchi fried rice]

1087
00:45:45,500 --> 00:45:46,380
[Jinwoo: Wow, that's gonna be good.]

1088
00:45:46,400 --> 00:45:48,800
[-Seungho: Feels like it's gonna overflow.
-Yongkyu: Right?]

1089
00:45:48,800 --> 00:45:51,210
[Hyeyeon: But I'm sure you'll do great.]

1090
00:45:51,210 --> 00:45:52,810
[Seungho: There's still half left, right?]

1091
00:45:52,810 --> 00:45:54,940
[Hyeyeon: I'll go over there
and stir-fry the kimchi first.]

1092
00:45:54,940 --> 00:45:56,810
[-Yongkyu: Okay.
-Jinwoo: Nice.]

1093
00:45:56,810 --> 00:45:58,680
[-Jinwoo: I'll try stir-frying it.
-Hyeyeon: Sure.]

1094
00:45:58,680 --> 00:46:00,550
[Yongkyu accepts the challenge]

1095
00:46:00,650 --> 00:46:02,790
[Yongkyu: Just put the cheese
on top, right?]

1096
00:46:02,790 --> 00:46:04,650
[-Jinwoo: Oh, okay.
-Hyeyeon: Ah, this portion?]

1097
00:46:04,650 --> 00:46:07,320
[Hyeyeon: He doesn't want
cheese on his own portion!]

1098
00:46:07,320 --> 00:46:09,190
[Jinwoo: Right, he doesn't
want cheese on his.]

1099
00:46:09,280 --> 00:46:10,060
Exactly.

1100
00:46:11,330 --> 00:46:13,460
[Yongkyu: No, no, no. I want to
try different flavors.]

1101
00:46:13,460 --> 00:46:14,800
[Jinwoo: Wait, what...]

1102
00:46:14,800 --> 00:46:16,000
[-Seungho: His reaction was delayed.
-Hyeyeon: He's buffering.]

1103
00:46:17,420 --> 00:46:21,260
[As Yongkyu's multi-flavor kimchi fried rice
gradually takes shape...]

1104
00:46:17,540 --> 00:46:18,540
-I want multiple flavors.
-No, no.

1105
00:46:18,540 --> 00:46:21,070
-He didn't deny it.
-I want multiple flavors!

1106
00:46:21,380 --> 00:46:23,220
Let me try. I'll stir-fry it.

1107
00:46:21,860 --> 00:46:25,980
[The cooking newbies start making
cheese kimchi fried rice]

1108
00:46:23,220 --> 00:46:24,550
What's up? You nervous?

1109
00:46:24,900 --> 00:46:25,940
It smells so good.

1110
00:46:26,380 --> 00:46:28,700
[Hyeyeon: It's gonna be delicious.]

1111
00:46:29,680 --> 00:46:31,900
[-Hyeyeon: Oh~ You're doing great!
-Jinwoo: Really?]

1112
00:46:31,460 --> 00:46:31,980
Yes.

1113
00:46:31,900 --> 00:46:34,290
[Gently...]
[Jinwoo: Am I a natural? Huh?]

1114
00:46:35,630 --> 00:46:37,230
[Yongkyu: It's burning, burning,
burning! Stir it faster!]

1115
00:46:37,230 --> 00:46:38,030
[Yongkyu: It's sticking! It's sticking!]

1116
00:46:38,030 --> 00:46:39,630
[Jinwoo: I need to stir faster?]
[Yongkyu: Yes!]

1117
00:46:40,700 --> 00:46:43,370
[-Jinwoo: Ah, I'm so anxious right now!
-Yongkyu: It's gonna stick, it's gonna stick!]

1118
00:46:43,370 --> 00:46:44,440
[-Jinwoo: Ah, I'm so nervous!
-Hyeyeon: You nervous?]

1119
00:46:44,440 --> 00:46:45,500
[Jinwoo: I'm so nervous!]

1120
00:46:45,500 --> 00:46:47,110
[Hyeyeon: Pass it to Seungho.]

1121
00:46:47,110 --> 00:46:48,970
[Jinwoo: No, it's okay. I'll keep going.]

1122
00:46:49,510 --> 00:46:52,440
[Seungho: You're scared mine
won't taste good?]

1123
00:46:52,440 --> 00:46:54,310
[Jinwoo: No~]

1124
00:46:54,850 --> 00:46:56,180
[Hyeyeon: Wow, that's a lot.]

1125
00:46:56,180 --> 00:46:57,520
[-Hyeyeon: It's like the cook soldier.
-Yongkyu: That's right. We've got so much.]

1126
00:47:01,250 --> 00:47:03,920
[Jinwoo: Add some cheese
and it'll be perfect.]

1127
00:47:03,920 --> 00:47:05,260
[Hyeyeon: Wanna taste it?]

1128
00:47:05,260 --> 00:47:07,660
[Jinwoo: But... can we actually
eat this right now?]

1129
00:47:07,660 --> 00:47:10,220
[Yongkyu: Gotta taste it to
adjust the seasoning.]

1130
00:47:10,220 --> 00:47:12,220
[Mmm~]

1131
00:47:12,730 --> 00:47:14,200
[Jinwoo: How is it?]

1132
00:47:14,200 --> 00:47:15,670
[Hyeyeon: I think we added a bit
too much oyster sauce.]

1133
00:47:16,470 --> 00:47:18,600
[-Jinwoo: You try it.
-Hyeyeon: Then I'll use a new spoon...]

1134
00:47:18,600 --> 00:47:20,470
[Jinwoo: Ah, just use the same one.]

1135
00:47:20,470 --> 00:47:23,300
[Seungho: Why are you
ignoring my opinion?]

1136
00:47:20,820 --> 00:47:23,150
-I... I—
-Why are you ignoring what I said?

1137
00:47:23,300 --> 00:47:25,900
[Jinwoo: Sorry.]

1138
00:47:25,900 --> 00:47:27,860
[Yongkyu: Did you eat the part
that wasn't fully cooked?]

1139
00:47:27,860 --> 00:47:29,020
[Yongkyu: Did you eat the part
that wasn't fried properly?]

1140
00:47:29,020 --> 00:47:31,950
[-Seungho: I'm the one eating it...
-Jinwoo: Sorry, I'll get you a new spoon.]

1141
00:47:31,950 --> 00:47:34,890
[Seungho: It's fine, it's fine...
I was just curious.]

1142
00:47:33,500 --> 00:47:34,340
Yeah, right.

1143
00:47:34,890 --> 00:47:36,490
[Hyeyeon: I was trying to
scoop some for myself...]

1144
00:47:36,490 --> 00:47:38,090
[Jinwoo: Got it.]

1145
