01:04:55,940 --> 01:04:58,070
[Sujin: You haven't even memorized our names yet.]

1591
01:04:57,340 --> 01:04:58,070
I know, right?

1592
01:04:58,070 --> 01:05:00,740
[Eunchae: Ah... I know your names now.
Sujin: Take your time.]

1593
01:05:00,740 --> 01:05:01,280
[Eunchae: Yeah, I will.]

1594
01:05:01,280 --> 01:05:03,950
[Jinwoo: Quick round of MBTI, let's go.]

1595
01:05:03,950 --> 01:05:05,010
[Eunchae: Starting from here.]

1596
01:05:05,010 --> 01:05:07,420
[Sujin: You know mine. What is it?]

1597
01:05:05,580 --> 01:05:06,500
Say it.

1598
01:05:06,860 --> 01:05:07,420
She forgot.

1599
01:05:07,420 --> 01:05:09,550
[Eunchae: INTP.
Sujin: Correct.]

1600
01:05:08,580 --> 01:05:09,300
Right?

1601
01:05:09,550 --> 01:05:11,420
[Seungho: I'm an ESTP.]

1602
01:05:11,420 --> 01:05:13,020
[Jinwoo: ENFP.]

1603
01:05:13,020 --> 01:05:15,160
[Hyeyeon: I'm an ESTP.]

1604
01:05:15,160 --> 01:05:17,560
[Yongkyu: I'm an INFJ.]

1605
01:05:17,830 --> 01:05:20,230
[Chaebe: INTP.]

1606
01:05:20,230 --> 01:05:22,630
[Heejin: I'm an INFJ.]

1607
01:05:22,630 --> 01:05:25,570
[Hyeyeon: Did you get all that?
Eunchae: That was way too fast.]

1608
01:05:25,570 --> 01:05:28,240
[Jinwoo: I didn't get it either.
Heejin: Just get a general vibe.]

1609
01:05:28,240 --> 01:05:29,840
[Hyeyeon: I only remembered the other ESTP.]

1610
01:05:29,840 --> 01:05:31,970
[Seungho and Hyeyeon are both ESTPs]

1611
01:05:29,860 --> 01:05:32,240
-Me too.
-I only remember the one that matches mine.

1612
01:05:32,240 --> 01:05:33,840
[I only remember the one like me, too.]

1613
01:05:33,840 --> 01:05:35,980
[Chaebe is also an INTP as Sujin]

1614
01:05:35,980 --> 01:05:38,650
[Sujin: It seems like there are two of each type.]

1615
01:05:39,180 --> 01:05:41,660
[Heejin and Yongkyu are both INFJs]

1616
01:05:39,420 --> 01:05:40,740
-Yeah. -ESTP and INFJ.

1617
01:05:40,740 --> 01:05:41,820
Both of you are INFJs.

1618
01:05:41,660 --> 01:05:44,220
[Jinwoo: No ENFP.]

1619
01:05:44,240 --> 01:05:45,700
[Jinwoo: No other ENFPs, I'm the only ENFP here.]

1620
01:05:45,700 --> 01:05:47,260
[Sujin: You can easily do the work of two.]

1621
01:05:47,260 --> 01:05:49,340
[Jinwoo: Oh, I could do that.
Sujin: Then you're your own partner.]

1622
01:05:48,580 --> 01:05:49,220
Oh.

1623
01:05:49,340 --> 01:05:51,700
[Eunchae: An ENFP can pull off the work
of two people alone, is that right?]

1624
01:05:51,720 --> 01:05:53,580
[Sujin: Of course.]

1625
01:05:53,580 --> 01:05:55,820
[Jinwoo: Are you guys putting pressure on me?]

1626
01:05:54,220 --> 01:05:55,140
No, no.

1627
01:05:55,820 --> 01:05:58,460
[Sujin: It means you're doing great.]

1628
01:05:57,140 --> 01:05:58,260
-Really? -Yes.

1629
01:05:59,040 --> 01:06:01,180
[Jinwoo: Thank you.]

1630
01:06:01,580 --> 01:06:02,840
A mission has arrived.

1631
01:06:04,540 --> 01:06:06,220
[Mission]

1632
01:06:06,220 --> 01:06:07,460
[Mission: Who'll be your roommate at
the BI-LIVE house? Please choose your roommate.]

1633
01:06:06,340 --> 01:06:07,820
-We have to pick roommates? -This is so sudden.

1634
01:06:07,460 --> 01:06:09,860
[Jinwoo: Are we supposed
to discuss it and decide?]

1635
01:06:10,920 --> 01:06:14,650
[Hyeyeon: Mission cards container is
next to the plushie.]

1636
01:06:16,520 --> 01:06:18,660
[The roommates who lived together
for a week in BI-LIVE]

1637
01:06:18,660 --> 01:06:21,780
[Hyeyeon: Oh, this one.]

1638
01:06:20,380 --> 01:06:21,180
Oh, it's this.

1639
01:06:21,780 --> 01:06:22,740
[So nervous]

1640
01:06:22,740 --> 01:06:25,600
[Hyeyeon: Oh, it's for drawing lots.
Seungho: A lottery? So fun!]

1641
01:06:26,400 --> 01:06:28,000
[Sujin: So they're going to be mixed up?]

1642
01:06:28,270 --> 01:06:29,600
[Yongkyu: Ah, really.]

1643
01:06:29,600 --> 01:06:31,200
[Eunchae: It's totally random.
Sujin: What should we do?]

1644
01:06:31,200 --> 01:06:32,800
[Hyeyeon: Drawing a wooden stick
with a number on it.]

1645
01:06:32,800 --> 01:06:36,010
[Hyeyeon: Starting from Number 1,
you can just choose the room you want.]

1646
01:06:36,010 --> 01:06:38,410
[Hyeyeon: The main building has a quad room.]

1647
01:06:38,410 --> 01:06:41,080
[Hyeyeon: And the annex over there
has a triple room and a single room.]

1648
01:06:42,680 --> 01:06:44,550
[Hyeyeon: Those are the rules.]

1649
01:06:43,460 --> 01:06:44,320
In that case...

1650
01:06:46,420 --> 01:06:47,750
[Eunchae: First up is Sujin,]

1651
01:06:47,750 --> 01:06:50,690
[Eunchae: since my first date was with her.]

1652
01:06:50,690 --> 01:06:53,360
[Eunchae: She's also the person
I've talked to the most.]

1653
01:06:54,430 --> 01:06:57,360
[Sujin: I want to pick Hyeyeon and Heejin.
The three of us.]

1654
01:06:57,360 --> 01:06:58,960
[Sujin: We should stay in the triple room.]

1655
01:06:58,960 --> 01:07:02,170
[Sujin: First, Hyeyeon and I already
know each other, so we're close.]

1656
01:07:02,170 --> 01:07:04,300
[Sujin: And I'm also quite interested in Heejin.]

1657
01:07:04,300 --> 01:07:06,970
[Sujin: If we could be roommates,
that would be great.]

1658
01:07:07,510 --> 01:07:09,640
[Heejin: I thought about a double room.]

1659
01:07:09,640 --> 01:07:12,840
[Heejin: But I never expected a triple
or a quad room sharing situation.]

1660
01:07:12,840 --> 01:07:16,580
[Heejin: And I brought a lot of luggage.]

1661
01:07:16,580 --> 01:07:19,250
[Heejin: It'll be inconvenient
if I unpack everything.]

1662
01:07:19,250 --> 01:07:21,120
[Heejin: So I want a single room.]

1663
01:07:21,780 --> 01:07:24,700
[Hyeyeon: Well, since you worked the hardest
cooking today,

1664
01:07:24,700 --> 01:07:25,660
-you should draw first. -Yongky really worked...

1665
01:07:25,460 --> 01:07:27,340
[Yongkyu: Me?]

1666
01:07:25,660 --> 01:07:26,420
-Me? -Yes.

1667
01:07:27,340 --> 01:07:30,190
[Hyeyeon: No hesitation at all.
Yongkyu: Yes.]

1668
01:07:30,780 --> 01:07:31,530
[Hyeyeon: Make sure you get a good one!]

1669
01:07:31,530 --> 01:07:33,660
[Hyeyeon: Keep it to yourself for now.]

1670
01:07:33,660 --> 01:07:36,870
[Jinwoo: That's right.
Seungho: That's the most fun way to play.]

1671
01:07:37,940 --> 01:07:41,140
[Hyeyeon: Since I worked the second hardest,
should I draw next?]

1672
01:07:44,070 --> 01:07:47,550
[Hyeyeon: The newcomer.
Jinwoo: The newcomer.]

1673
01:07:50,210 --> 01:07:56,620
[Everyone draws a stick in their own way]

1674
01:07:56,890 --> 01:08:00,360
[Heejin and Sujin are left with the final draws]

1675
01:07:57,260 --> 01:07:58,460
Which one do you want?

1676
01:07:58,820 --> 01:08:00,460
-This one. -This one?

1677
01:08:00,360 --> 01:08:02,490
[Heejin: I'll take that... wait, no.]

1678
01:08:02,380 --> 01:08:03,260
-I want this one. -This one?

1679
01:08:02,490 --> 01:08:03,560
[Heejin: I want this one.]

1680
01:08:03,260 --> 01:08:04,540
-Yes. -I'll take this one then.

1681
01:08:03,560 --> 01:08:05,020
[Sujin: I'll take this one then.]

1682
01:08:05,540 --> 01:08:06,500
Thank you.

1683
01:08:08,900 --> 01:08:12,900
[Hyeyeon: Shall we reveal the numbers
starting with Sujin?]

1684
01:08:12,900 --> 01:08:13,970
[Sujin: Okay.]

1685
01:08:13,970 --> 01:08:15,840
[Hyeyeon: What's your number?
Sujin: I got number 1.]

1686
01:08:16,420 --> 01:08:18,510
[What? Amazing.]

1687
01:08:18,510 --> 01:08:20,910
[Heejin: Hold on.]

1688
01:08:19,620 --> 01:08:21,550
-You're so lucky. -First of all...

1689
01:08:23,580 --> 01:08:25,180
[Hyeyeon: Seungho, what's your number?]

1690
01:08:25,180 --> 01:08:27,850
[Seungho: I got number 6.]

1691
01:08:26,460 --> 01:08:26,990
Number 9?

1692
01:08:29,189 --> 01:08:30,790
[Jinwoo: I got number 5.]

1693
01:08:31,060 --> 01:08:33,189
[Eunchae: I got number 2.]

1694
01:08:33,189 --> 01:08:34,790
[Hyeyeon: I got number 3.]

1695
01:08:34,790 --> 01:08:36,930
[Yongkyu: I got number 8.]

1696
01:08:36,930 --> 01:08:40,130
[Yongkyu, who drew first, got number 8]

1697
01:08:37,740 --> 01:08:40,180
I was the very first to draw.

1698
01:08:40,130 --> 01:08:42,000
[Chaebe: I got number 4.]

1699
01:08:42,800 --> 01:08:44,130
[Chaebe: I think number 4 is great.]

1700
01:08:44,130 --> 01:08:47,660
[Chaebe: It's not too far back,
and it's not too far forward.]

1701
01:08:47,660 --> 01:08:51,609
[Chaebe: A middle number
with less pressure. It's really great.]

1702
01:08:52,939 --> 01:08:54,810
[Heejin: I got number 7.]

1703
01:08:54,810 --> 01:08:57,479
[Sujin: Heejin originally picked this one.]

1704
01:08:57,479 --> 01:08:59,350
[Heejin: I know.
Sujin: And then she swapped with me.]

1705
01:08:59,350 --> 01:09:00,420
[Heejin: Yes.]

1706
01:08:59,620 --> 01:09:00,380
A mixture of joy and sorrow.

1707
01:09:00,380 --> 01:09:01,380
-Their fates swapped. -Exactly.

1708
01:09:00,950 --> 01:09:03,890
[Heejin, whose number changed from 1 to 7]

1709
01:09:01,380 --> 01:09:02,180
Number 1 and 7.

1710
01:09:02,180 --> 01:09:03,939
-This is destiny. -Insane.

1711
01:09:03,890 --> 01:09:06,290
[Heejin: This is destiny.]

1712
01:09:06,290 --> 01:09:08,100
[Heejin: I'll just accept it gracefully.]

1713
01:09:08,100 --> 01:09:09,300
[Heejin: My intuition is always terrible.]

1714
01:09:09,300 --> 01:09:11,939
[Heejin: Ever since I got here,
I've made all the wrong choices.]

1715
01:09:11,939 --> 01:09:14,060
[Heejin: Judging by this...]

1716
01:09:14,060 --> 01:09:16,100
[Heejin: Maybe my feelings about Seungho
was just an illusion, too.]

1717
01:09:16,100 --> 01:09:18,500
[Heejin: We're back to this topic again...]

1718
01:09:18,500 --> 01:09:21,170
[Hyeyeon: Shall we go check out the rooms?]

1719
01:09:18,899 --> 01:09:21,260
-Let's go look at the rooms. -Room tour!

1720
01:09:21,170 --> 01:09:22,770
[Sujin: Do we go straight up?]

1721
01:09:22,770 --> 01:09:24,100
[Yongkyu: Yeah, right up this way.]

1722
01:09:24,640 --> 01:09:27,840
[Who will become roommates
for the week spent at BI-LIVE?]

1723
01:09:27,840 --> 01:09:30,240
[Sujin: Looks like Heejin wants the single room.]

1724
01:09:30,240 --> 01:09:32,910
[Heejin: Huh? No, I don't?]

1725
01:09:32,910 --> 01:09:34,779
[Sujin: How lonely would that be?]

1726
01:09:34,779 --> 01:09:36,380
[Heejin: How lonely would that be?]

1727
01:09:36,380 --> 01:09:40,390
[Sujin: But enjoying solitude is also...]

1728
01:09:40,649 --> 01:09:43,319
[Sujin: Is this the quad room?]

1729
01:09:43,319 --> 01:09:46,529
[Sujin: Excuse me, don't tell me
we have to share the same bed?]

1730
01:09:46,529 --> 01:09:47,859
[Heejin: It looks like it.]

1731
01:09:50,529 --> 01:09:52,399
[The Quad Room]

1732
01:09:55,870 --> 01:09:59,870
[A spacious quad room located next
to floor-to-ceiling windows]

1733
01:10:00,940 --> 01:10:02,280
[Yongkyu: It looks like a 2-1-1 layout.]

1734
01:10:02,280 --> 01:10:05,750
[Hyeyeon: Over there is the single room.
Yongkyu: It's a 2-1-1 layout.]

1735
01:10:05,750 --> 01:10:07,080
[Seungho: It's so warm in here.]

1736
01:10:07,080 --> 01:10:09,220
[Jinwoo: This is the triple room!]

1737
01:10:09,750 --> 01:10:12,150
[The Triple Room]

1738
01:10:15,890 --> 01:10:18,560
[A cozy space for open and pleasant conversations]

1739
01:10:20,430 --> 01:10:22,830
[With comfortable beds]

1740
01:10:24,430 --> 01:10:26,300
[Sujin: The single room is so nice.]

1741
01:10:30,300 --> 01:10:32,170
[Sujin: The single room is amazing.]

1742
01:10:32,710 --> 01:10:34,840
[The Single Room]

1743
01:10:40,180 --> 01:10:42,050
[Eunchae: Wow, this is incredible.
Hyeyeon: Is it good?]

1744
01:10:42,660 --> 01:10:43,540
-What? -Hold on.

1745
01:10:43,540 --> 01:10:44,580
What's going on?

1746
01:10:45,250 --> 01:10:48,460
[A single single room
to be enjoyed leisurely alone]

1747
01:10:45,260 --> 01:10:47,180
-What is it? -What is it?

1748
01:10:47,180 --> 01:10:48,900
It looks even bigger than the triple room.

1749
01:10:48,720 --> 01:10:50,860
[Sujin: Cannot hide the joy.]

1750
01:10:50,860 --> 01:10:52,730
[Yongkyu: I don't think I'll get the chance.]

1751
01:10:52,730 --> 01:10:55,660
[Sujin: Most likely.
Yongkyu: It won't be my turn, right?]

1752
01:10:55,660 --> 01:10:58,600
[Sujin: Everyone seems to
have their eyes on the single room.]

1753
01:10:58,600 --> 01:11:00,200
[Seungho: At first, I wanted the quad room.]

1754
01:11:00,200 --> 01:11:02,600
[Seungho: But the single room
is much better than I imagined.]

1755
01:11:02,600 --> 01:11:04,210
[Seungho: I can always invite
other people over anyway.]

1756
01:11:04,210 --> 01:11:07,680
[Seungho: So I want to live in a single room
or a quad room.]

1757
01:11:11,150 --> 01:11:13,280
[The lively room tour comes to an end...]

1758
01:11:15,680 --> 01:11:20,220
[Seungho: Did you choose me, hyung?
Jinwoo: Of course.]

1759
01:11:18,320 --> 01:11:19,020
Really?

1760
01:11:20,220 --> 01:11:23,420
[Jinwoo: Seungho, what about you?
Seungho: Me too.]

1761
01:11:27,960 --> 01:11:30,900
[Seungho: Honestly, I didn't
expect this to happen.]

1762
01:11:30,900 --> 01:11:36,770
Seungho: I thought if two people
picked each other, they'd automatically pair up.]

1763
01:11:34,420 --> 01:11:36,220
I know, right?

1764
01:11:36,220 --> 01:11:37,080
All of a sudden.

1765
01:11:37,840 --> 01:11:40,510
[Jinwoo: Shall we sit face to face?
Seungho: Sure.]

1766
01:11:40,510 --> 01:11:47,450
[Jinwoo: Let me pour you a drink,
since you invited me. Thanks.]

1767
01:11:47,450 --> 01:11:49,850
[Jinwoo: It felt very romantic.]

1768
01:11:49,850 --> 01:11:53,050
[Jinwoo: And there were so many
melancholic lights around us.]

1769
01:11:53,050 --> 01:11:56,520
[Jinwoo: I was looking forward
to what we'd talk about here.]

1770
01:11:56,520 --> 01:11:59,730
[Jinwoo: Feeling great.]

1771
01:12:00,790 --> 01:12:03,460
[Seungho: I want to pour it like a waiter.]

1772
01:12:03,460 --> 01:12:05,600
[Seungho: It's not that awkward anymore.]

1773
01:12:05,600 --> 01:12:08,540
[Seungho: But since we entered in
this kind of setup...]

1774
01:12:08,540 --> 01:12:13,340
[Seungho: It feels a little awkward again,
when we first walked in.]

1775
01:12:13,870 --> 01:12:17,610
[Seungho & Jinwoo spending time together.
What kind of night will they have?]
